# Terms of Service for BNO One Stop

**Last Updated:** January 2026

## 1. Acceptance of Terms

By downloading, installing, and using the BNO One Stop application ("App"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, do not use the App.

## 2. Description of Service

BNO One Stop is a mobile application designed to help British National (Overseas) visa holders track their immigration status, calculate ILR eligibility, manage absence records, and organize immigration-related documents and checklists.

